    "section_faq_HQknCD": {
      "type": "section-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "category_HTyKAt": {
          "type": "category",
          "settings": {
            "title": "General Questions"
          }
        },
        "article_UP3xzn": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What makes Fenceworks trampolines safer than other brands?",
            "text": "<p>At Fenceworks, safety is more than just a feature — it’s a commitment rooted in over 50 years of serving local families. That’s why we exclusively carry <strong>ACON trampolines</strong>, the gold standard in premium safety and engineering. </p><p>As a <strong>third-generation family business</strong>, Fenceworks goes beyond just selling a trampoline — we provide <strong>expert consultation, professional installation, and long-term support</strong> to make sure your family’s trampoline is safe from day one and remains that way for years.</p><p>When you choose Fenceworks and ACON, you're not just getting a trampoline — you're getting <strong>peace of mind, local service, and a product built to last.</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "article_CyRX4q": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How are Fenceworks trampolines designed for safety and durability?",
            "text": "<p>At Fenceworks, we proudly offer <strong>ACON trampolines</strong>, engineered for unmatched safety and long-term durability — ideal for active families in the Chicago area who want the best for their kids.</p><p>Unlike traditional trampolines that cut corners with lightweight frames or thin padding, <strong>ACON trampolines are built from the ground up for performance and protection</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "article_BPbqJi": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do Fenceworks trampolines require professional installation?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, we provide <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/pages/trampoline-installation/\">professional installation services</a> to ensure that your trampoline is set up safely and correctly, adhering to all local safety standards.</p>"
          }
        },
        "category_HUe8Nt": {
          "type": "category",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Safety Features"
          }
        },
        "article_Bpwt3W": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What specific safety features do Fenceworks trampolines have?",
            "text": "<p><strong>Heavy-duty galvanized steel frame</strong> – Rust-resistant and engineered to handle years of use in all seasons.<br/><strong>No single-user weight limit</strong> – Perfect for kids, teens, and adults. Jump with confidence, not limitations.<br/><strong>High-tension, pre-galvanized springs</strong> – Deliver consistent, responsive bounce without losing elasticity over time.</p><p><strong>Thick spring and edge padding</strong> – Fully covers springs and frame to prevent injuries.<br/><strong>Reinforced safety enclosure</strong> – Tightly woven, UV-resistant net with padded poles and secure entry zipper.<br/><strong>Low injury risk bounce surface</strong> – Designed to reduce impact stress on joints for safer landings.</p><p><strong>UV-treated, cross-sewn polypropylene jump mat</strong> – Won’t fade, stretch, or tear under sun and rain.<br/><strong>Designed for year-round use</strong> – No need to disassemble in winter (though winter covers are available).</p><p><strong>Modular design: </strong>allows for easy add-ons as your family’s needs grow.</p>"
          }
        },
        "article_efPWAA": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can Fenceworks trampolines withstand harsh weather?",
            "text": "<p>Absolutely. Our trampolines are built to resist rain and UV damage, maintaining their integrity and safety through all seasons.</p>"
          }
        },
        "article_aDxJ8J": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is the weight limit for a Fenceworks trampoline?",
            "text": "<p>Our trampolines can support up to 295 lbs for single users, with robust construction that accommodates more weight for multiple users safely.</p>"
          }
        },
        "category_JTbnBY": {
          "type": "category",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Purchase & Installation"
          }
        },
        "article_ytYkHD": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How can I ensure the trampoline fits in my yard?",
            "text": "<p>We recommend at least 3-5 feet of clearance around the trampoline. Our team can help assess your space to ensure a perfect fit.</p>"
          }
        },
        "article_gRPz8E": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What makes the ACON trampolines line special?",
            "text": "<p>ACON trampolines stand out as one of the <strong>most premium, performance-driven trampolines in the world</strong> — and at Fenceworks, we’re proud to bring their full line directly to families across Chicagoland.<br/><br/>Designed in <strong>Finland</strong>, ACON trampolines are the result of <strong>decades of engineering focused on quality, safety, and bounce performance</strong>.<br/>Every model is built with precision, from frame to spring, ensuring a <strong>consistent and smooth jumping experience</strong> for all ages.</p><p><strong>Heavy-duty galvanized steel frames</strong>, <strong>UV-resistant materials</strong>, and <strong>high-performance polypropylene mats</strong> mean your trampoline will <strong>endure Chicago’s extreme seasons</strong> without rusting, fading, or stretching.</p>"
          }
        },
        "category_bMJVKK": {
          "type": "category",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Customer Experience"
          }
        },
        "article_tr6iiD": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I choose the right Fenceworks trampoline for my family?",
            "text": "<p>Our expert staff will guide you through selecting the perfect trampoline that fits your family's needs and ensures maximum safety and enjoyment.</p>"
          }
        },
        "article_W9yn36": {
          "type": "article",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What if I need help or have questions after purchasing?",
            "text": "<p>When you need assistance, you’re connecting directly with our dedicated team—not a call center. We’re here to provide real-time support and ensure your complete satisfaction.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
